name: Assault
display_help: Only the most insidious Mastermind could construct such an army. Cold and relentless, these Bots obey only one voice, and will execute any order without hesitation.

name: Droid
display_help: Only the most insidious Mastermind could construct such an army. Cold and relentless, these Bots obey only one voice, and will execute any order without hesitation.

name: Ghosts
display_help: Even when a person survives an encounter with a Ghost, he rarely escapes entirely unscathed. He will often find himself waking in the night, shuddering at the memory of a cold and lifeless touch.

name: Lich
display_help: The lich is an undead entity that, when alive, possessed many dark powers of his own. Perhaps it was a dark wizard, or powerful arch villain. Perhaps it was even a Necromancer. Now it only hungers for the souls of the living, and is quite good at feeding itself.

name: Protector
display_help: Only the most insidious Mastermind could construct such an army. Cold and relentless, these Bots obey only one voice, and will execute any order without hesitation.

name: Skeleton
display_help: Only the most battle hardened warriors filled with a lust for revenge will return as a Grave Knight. This undead warrior may be sentient, but it has no understanding of a living world now alien to him. It can only see its own bloodlust and thirst for vengeance. Only the most powerful Masterminds can control them.

name: Zombie
display_help: The walking dead may be slow and stupid, but wise heroes know better than to underestimate them. Even when a person survives an encounter with a zombie, he rarely escapes entirely unscathed. He will often find himself waking in the night, shuddering at the memory of a dry and lifeless touch.
